------------
-- README --
------------

This Perl script forwards received Syslog event to a Loggly input using HTTPS.
Loggly is a Cloud based log management solution. (http://www.loggly.com)

Default configuration file: /etc/syslog2loggly.cong
  apikey=xxxxx
  port=xxxxx

For more information, visit: 
http://blog.rootshell.be/2010/12/27/send-events-safely-to-the-loggly-cloud

Feel free to contribute to the script.
